headline: Buy These 5 Non-Tech Stocks for 2025 Amid Triple-Digit Returns in 2024
summary: Five non-tech stocks have more room to grow in 2025 despite triple-digit returns in 2024. These are; SFM, FIX, EME, VST, CVNA.
